title: CNN’s Don Lemon: Is Flynn Resignation a ‘Wake-Up Call’ for Trump White House?
text:
CNN’s Don Lemon: Is Flynn Resignation a ‘Wake-Up Call’ for Trump White House? by Josh Feldman | 11:47 pm, February 13th, 2017 
CNN’s Don Lemon asked Rick Santorum tonight if Michael Flynn ‘s resignation is a “wake-up call” for the Trump White House that something needs to change. 
Lemon was going off a point made by CNN’s Mark Preston , who suggested minutes earlier that this could potentially open the floodgates for more personnel changes. 
Santorum, who thinks the resignation was appropriate, said this was a serious “major problem” compared to more minor issues that have been rumored about other Trump administration officials. 
That being said, he added, “if the rocky road continues,” it wouldn’t be a surprise to see more personnel changes. 
Watch above, via CNN.
